---
// Economics section — dark inset card
const items = [
  ['Customer profile', 'One bank, 1,000 call-center agents'],
  ['Calls processed', '20 calls/agent/day × 5 min × 30 days'],
  ['Audio per month', '3,000,000 minutes'],
  ['Foggy revenue', '$36,000/month transcription'],
  ['Classification add-on', '$3,450/month on 150M tx queries'],
];
---

<section id="economics" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-foggy-bg">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-bold tracking-tight text-foggy-ink" style="font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);">
      The economics.
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-[20px] text-foggy-ink-light leading-relaxed">
      Foggy doesn't have to build data centers, doesn't have to buy GPUs, and doesn't have to route data internationally. That's why the unit economics work in markets where the hyperscalers' don't.
    </p>

    <!-- Dark bank pilot card -->
    <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl border border-foggy-line bg-foggy-night p-10">
      <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-foggy-text-on-dark">A single bank pilot, sketched out</h3>

      <!-- Hero number -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <div class="text-[48px] font-bold text-foggy-green-glow leading-none">~$475,000</div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-[12px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-foggy-text-muted-dark">Total per customer / year gross</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Key/value list -->
      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-0">
        {items.map(([label, value]) => (
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-foggy-line py-3 text-[15px]">
            <span class="text-foggy-text-muted-dark">{label}</span>
            <span class="text-foggy-text-on-dark font-bold">{value}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-[14px] italic text-foggy-text-muted-dark">
        Roughly 30 large banks across Kenya, Rwanda, and Tanzania fit this profile. Sub-Saharan Africa cloud AI is a $3-4B market growing 27% annually (Fortune Business Insights).
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
